Last Updated: 04-12-2025

GrooZo delivers food from partnered restaurants directly to your doorstep through our delivery partners.

1. Delivery Time
  - Food will be delivered within 60 minutes on an average, depending on:
  - Restaurant preparation time
  - Distance between restaurant and delivery address
  - Traffic and weather conditions
  - Availability of delivery partners
  - Real-time tracking is available within the app.

2. Delivery Areas
  - GrooZo currently delivers within designated service zones. If your location falls outside the delivery radius, the app will notify you before placing the order.

3. Delivery Charges
  Delivery fees may vary based on:
  - Distance
  - Peak hours
  All charges are visible before completing your order.

4. Delivery Responsibility
  - Restaurants are responsible for preparing and packing the food.
  - Delivery partners are responsible for safe and timely transit.
  - GrooZo is not responsible for delays caused by unforeseen circumstances (traffic, weather, festivals, roadblocks, etc.).

5. Failed Delivery
  Delivery may fail if:
  - The user does not respond to calls/messages
  - Incorrect or unreachable address is provided
  - Security restrictions prevent entry
  In such cases, no refund will be issued unless the failure was due to a genuine operational error.

6. Order Verification
  - Delivery partners may verify the order via OTP or call before handover to ensure accurate delivery.
